---
import Base from "~/layouts/Base.astro";

const LAST_UPDATE = "2026-04-22";
---

<Base
  title="Mentions légales — Manager"
  description="Mentions légales du site managerladger.com : éditeur, hébergeur, contact."
>
  <section class="legal">
    <div class="legal__inner">

      <span class="eyebrow legal__eyebrow">
        <span data-lang="en">Legal notice</span>
        <span data-lang="fr">Mentions légales</span>
      </span>

      <h1 class="legal__title">
        <span data-lang="en">Legal <em>notice.</em></span>
        <span data-lang="fr">Mentions <em>légales.</em></span>
      </h1>

      <p class="legal__lede">
        <span data-lang="en">Required by article 6-III of the French LCEN (2004-575) for any public website published in France.</span>
        <span data-lang="fr">Requises par l'article 6-III de la LCEN (loi 2004-575) pour tout site web publié en France.</span>
      </p>

      <p class="legal__meta">
        <span data-lang="en">Last updated: {LAST_UPDATE}</span>
        <span data-lang="fr">Dernière mise à jour : {LAST_UPDATE}</span>
      </p>

      <!-- 01 — Éditeur -->
      <section class="legal__section">
        <span class="legal__num">Nº 01</span>
        <h2 class="legal__h2">
          <span data-lang="en">Publisher</span>
          <span data-lang="fr">Éditeur du site</span>
        </h2>
        <dl class="legal__dl">
          <dt data-lang="en">Name</dt>
          <dt data-lang="fr">Nom</dt>
          <dd>Auxance Jourdan</dd>

          <dt data-lang="en">Status</dt>
          <dt data-lang="fr">Statut</dt>
          <dd data-lang="en">
            Individual — non-professional publisher (French LCEN art. 6-III-2).
            Sole-trader (auto-entrepreneur) registration is pending; this page will be updated with SIREN / SIRET as soon as they are issued.
          </dd>
          <dd data-lang="fr">
            Particulier — éditeur non-professionnel (art. 6-III-2 LCEN).
            Une immatriculation auto-entrepreneur est en cours ; cette page sera mise à jour avec le SIREN / SIRET dès leur délivrance.
          </dd>

          <dt data-lang="en">Postal address</dt>
          <dt data-lang="fr">Adresse postale</dt>
          <dd data-lang="en">
            Kept confidential under article 6-III-2 LCEN. Personal identification details are disclosed to the host (see below) and available to the competent authorities on legitimate request.
          </dd>
          <dd data-lang="fr">
            Non divulguée au titre de l'article 6-III-2 de la LCEN. Les éléments d'identification personnelle sont communiqués à l'hébergeur (voir ci-dessous) et accessibles aux autorités compétentes sur demande légitime.
          </dd>

          <dt data-lang="en">Email</dt>
          <dt data-lang="fr">Email</dt>
          <dd><a href="mailto:auxance.jourdan@proton.me">auxance.jourdan@proton.me</a></dd>

          <dt data-lang="en">Publication director</dt>
          <dt data-lang="fr">Directeur de la publication</dt>
          <dd>Auxance Jourdan</dd>
        </dl>
      </section>

      <!-- 02 — Hébergeur -->
      <section class="legal__section">
        <span class="legal__num">Nº 02</span>
        <h2 class="legal__h2">
          <span data-lang="en">Host</span>
          <span data-lang="fr">Hébergeur</span>
        </h2>
        <dl class="legal__dl">
          <dt data-lang="en">Provider</dt>
          <dt data-lang="fr">Prestataire</dt>
          <dd>Cloudflare, Inc.</dd>

          <dt data-lang="en">Address</dt>
          <dt data-lang="fr">Adresse</dt>
          <dd>101 Townsend Street, San Francisco, CA 94107, USA</dd>

          <dt data-lang="en">Service</dt>
          <dt data-lang="fr">Service</dt>
          <dd>Cloudflare Pages</dd>

          <dt data-lang="en">Phone</dt>
          <dt data-lang="fr">Téléphone</dt>
          <dd>+1 (650) 319-8930</dd>
        </dl>
      </section>

      <!-- 03 — Propriété intellectuelle -->
      <section class="legal__section">
        <span class="legal__num">Nº 03</span>
        <h2 class="legal__h2">
          <span data-lang="en">Intellectual property</span>
          <span data-lang="fr">Propriété intellectuelle</span>
        </h2>
        <p data-lang="en">
          The content of this website (text, typography, graphic identity, source code, screenshots) is the exclusive property of the publisher, except where noted otherwise. Any reproduction, representation or redistribution, in whole or in part, without prior written consent is prohibited and may constitute infringement under articles L.335-2 and following of the French Intellectual Property Code.
        </p>
        <p data-lang="fr">
          Les contenus de ce site (textes, typographie, identité graphique, code source, captures d'écran) sont la propriété exclusive de l'éditeur, sauf mention contraire. Toute reproduction, représentation ou rediffusion, partielle ou totale, sans autorisation écrite préalable est interdite et peut constituer une contrefaçon au sens des articles L.335-2 et suivants du Code de la propriété intellectuelle.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- 04 — Liens sortants -->
      <section class="legal__section">
        <span class="legal__num">Nº 04</span>
        <h2 class="legal__h2">
          <span data-lang="en">Outbound links</span>
          <span data-lang="fr">Liens sortants</span>
        </h2>
        <p data-lang="en">
          Download buttons redirect to <a href="https://github.com/JAuxance/manager-releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com</a>, operated by GitHub, Inc. (a Microsoft Corporation subsidiary). The publisher is not responsible for the content of third-party sites reached through these links.
        </p>
        <p data-lang="fr">
          Les boutons de téléchargement redirigent vers <a href="https://github.com/JAuxance/manager-releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com</a>, exploité par GitHub, Inc. (filiale de Microsoft Corporation). L'éditeur décline toute responsabilité quant au contenu des sites tiers accessibles via ces liens.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- 05 — Contact -->
      <section class="legal__section">
        <span class="legal__num">Nº 05</span>
        <h2 class="legal__h2">Contact</h2>
        <p data-lang="en">
          For any request related to this website, write to <a href="mailto:auxance.jourdan@proton.me">auxance.jourdan@proton.me</a>.
        </p>
        <p data-lang="fr">
          Pour toute demande relative à ce site, écrire à <a href="mailto:auxance.jourdan@proton.me">auxance.jourdan@proton.me</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <a class="legal__back" href="/">
        <span class="legal__back-arrow" aria-hidden="true">←</span>
        <span data-lang="en">Back to Manager</span>
        <span data-lang="fr">Retour à Manager</span>
      </a>

    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .legal {
    background: var(--paper);
    padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 10rem) var(--gutter) clamp(4rem, 7vw, 6rem);
    min-height: 100dvh;
  }

  .legal__inner {
    max-width: 56rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-5);
  }

  .legal__eyebrow { color: var(--mute); }

  .legal__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw + 0.5rem, 6rem);
    font-weight: 200;
    line-height: 0.96;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
    padding-bottom: 0.08em;
  }
  .legal__title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--mute); }

  .legal__lede {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 0.75vw + 0.9rem, 1.4rem);
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--mute);
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 48ch;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .legal__meta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-caps);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mute);
    margin: var(--space-2) 0 var(--space-8);
  }

  .legal__section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 3fr);
    gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4rem);
    padding: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.5rem) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .legal__section:last-of-type { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }

  .legal__num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-caps);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mute);
  }

  .legal__h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2vw + 0.75rem, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 200;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
    grid-column: 2;
  }

  .legal__section > p {
    grid-column: 2;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 0.4vw + 0.9rem, 1.15rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-3);
    max-width: 62ch;
  }
  .legal__section > p + p { margin-top: var(--space-3); }
  .legal__section a {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .legal__dl {
    grid-column: 2;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(140px, 1fr) minmax(0, 2fr);
    gap: var(--space-3) var(--space-5);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 52rem;
  }
  .legal__dl dt {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-caps);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mute);
    align-self: baseline;
  }
  .legal__dl dd {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 0.3vw + 0.9rem, 1.1rem);
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .legal__back {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    padding: var(--space-3) 0;
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-caps);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    align-self: flex-start;
    transition: transform var(--dur-press) var(--ease-out);
  }
  .legal__back:hover .legal__back-arrow { transform: translateX(-4px); }
  .legal__back-arrow { transition: transform var(--dur-base) var(--ease-editorial); }
  .legal__back:active { transform: scale(0.97); }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .legal__section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-3);
    }
    .legal__h2, .legal__section > p, .legal__dl {
      grid-column: 1;
    }
    .legal__dl {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-1) 0;
    }
    .legal__dl dt { margin-top: var(--space-3); }
  }
</style>
